          <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>Groundwater Conservation Incentive Act of 2015</strong></p> <p>This bill amends the Internal Revenue Code to expand the tax deduction for soil and water conservation expenditures to include expenditures to reduce groundwater use and for the conversion from groundwater use to surface water use. </p>]]></text>
